360
00:32:26,094 --> 00:32:27,254
<font color=#FFFF00>Hai, Soo Ji.</font>

361
00:32:28,264 --> 00:32:29,423
<font color=#FFFF00>Pasang sabuk pengamanmu.</font>

362
00:32:29,923 --> 00:32:31,034
<font color=#FFFF00>Baik!</font>

363
00:32:36,733 --> 00:32:40,233
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau tidak menulis lagi?</font>

364
00:32:41,673 --> 00:32:42,943
<font color=#FFFF00>Maaf.</font>

365
00:32:44,274 --> 00:32:47,784
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku juga tidak menulis lagi.</font>

366
00:32:52,284 --> 00:32:54,784
<font color=#FFFF00>Boleh aku tanya alasannya?</font>

367
00:32:56,754 --> 00:32:58,124
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sudah menikah sekarang.</font>

368
00:32:58,754 --> 00:33:00,993
<font color=#FFFF00>Setelah menikah, aku memutuskan
