370
00:33:12,004 --> 00:33:14,473
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sudah menikah rupanya.</font>

371
00:33:15,074 --> 00:33:16,143
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

372
00:33:17,814 --> 00:33:20,544
<font color=#FFFF00>Maaf kau sampai datang
