373
00:33:24,044 --> 00:33:25,254
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau begitu, permisi.</font>

374
00:33:27,624 --> 00:33:28,953
<font color=#FFFF00>Silakan nikmati kopinya.</font>

375
00:33:33,794 --> 00:33:36,193
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi, Penulis Yoon.</font>

376
00:33:40,133 --> 00:33:41,564
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa alasan itu kedengarannya...</font>

377
00:33:42,233 --> 00:33:44,574
<font color=#FFFF00>...seperti alasan sedih menurutku?</font>

378
00:33:54,143 --> 00:33:56,183
<font color=#FFFF00>Terima kasih kopinya.</font>

379
00:33:59,653 --> 00:34:00,784
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau-kalau...,</font>

380
00:34:02,824 --> 00:34:05,423
<font color=#FFFF00>...kau ingin mengatakan yang sebenarnya
daripada kasih alasan yang menyedihkan...,</font>

381
00:34:05,923 --> 00:34:07,524
<font color=#FFFF00>...hubungi aku kapan saja.</font>

382
00:34:09,924 --> 00:34:11,593
<font color=#FFFF00>Walau kita tidak bekerja sama...,</font>

383
00:34:12,294 --> 00:34:14,064
<font color=#FFFF00>...kita bisa pergi keluar minum bersama.</font>

384
00:35:02,343 --> 00:35:04,654
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau marah sekali?</font>

385
00:35:10,154 --> 00:35:11,294
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa rencanamu?</font>

386
00:35:12,154 --> 00:35:13,294
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa maksudmu?</font>

387
00:35:13,493 --> 00:35:18,152
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mengantar ibumu pulang
