<font color=#FFFF00><i>...berbohong tentang perselingkuhan?</i></font>

444
00:39:38,924 --> 00:39:40,223
<font color=#FFFF00>Kurasa aku mengerti.</font>

445
00:39:41,163 --> 00:39:43,363
<font color=#FFFF00>Karena jika orang
