499
00:43:20,513 --> 00:43:23,413
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak, bukan seperti itu.</font>

500
00:43:23,413 --> 00:43:24,513
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukan?</font>

501
00:43:25,683 --> 00:43:27,654
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi itu memang berarti sesuatu.</font>

502
00:43:28,984 --> 00:43:30,854
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana hubungan kita
